{{>layouts/mypageheader}}
<div class="container">
    <div class="content">
        <div class="content_header">
            <h2>회원 탈퇴</h2>
            <p>
                회원 탈퇴를 원하시면 모든 문구을 알맞게 작성해주세요!
            </p>
            <p>
                ※주의※  회원 탈퇴 시 작성하셨던 모든 게시물들은 삭제됩니다!
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <form id="unregister-form" class="unregister">
                <fieldset>
                    <div class="section_private shadow p-3 mb-5 bg-body-tertiary rounded">
                        <legend>< 회원 탈퇴 > </legend>

                        <div class="id">
                            <input type="text" id="id" class="input input-id" name="userId" value title="id" placeholder="아이디 : ">
                        </div>

                        <div id="id-message" class="id-message"></div>

                        <div class="pw">
                            <input type="password" id="pw" class="input input-pw" name="password" value title="pw" placeholder="비밀번호 : ">
                        </div>

                        <div id="pw-message" class="pw-message"></div>

                        <div class="words">
                            <input type="text" id="words" class="input input-words" name="unregister" value title="words" placeholder="탈퇴하겠습니다">
                        </div>

                        <div id="words-message" class="word-message"></div>

                        <div class="un-btn">
                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-outline-primary">탈퇴</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </fieldset>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
{{>layouts/mypagefooter}}